Q_DESC:
Ram wants to propose his girlfriend Sita but he is very nervous.Being so nervous he came with a plan to pick a number randomly.The number picked by the Ram is sum of subarrays of the main array.So help Ram to find continous subarray which adds to a given number.

Input:
The first line of the input contains size of the array.
The second line consists elements of the array.
The third line contain the sum value to be searched.

Output:
The ouput contains index of the subarray.
If subarray not found print "-1"
